2011-03-30 # 1.0

[NEW] Redesigned Operation API.

[FIX] Only the admin can access the "active" page.




2011-01-07 # 0.1.1

[NEW] The ids of the enabled modules are now saved in "%repository.cache/core/enabled_modules" as a
JSON string.




2010-09-23 # 0.1.0

[NEW] There is now two views to manage "actives" and "inactives" modules. 

[FIX] Newly added modules were activated by default because we were disabling modules using a
list of modules to disable. We are now using a list of enabled modules, modules missing from the
list are now disabled, except for mandatory modules.